tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The table summarizes customers who visited a car dealership in the last month by age and number of visits they made to the dealership. If a customer from the last month is selected at random, what is the probability that the selected customer is at least <math alttext=\"40\"><mn>40</mn>\n</math> years old?&nbsp;</p>",
